Originally a construction drone, the F has since evolved its robust hull for the rigours of interstellar battle. It is now the core fighter for the Terraformer fleet, its slow speed being easily balanced by its sturdy nature, allowing it to absorb all the damage from smaller faster ships while it unleashes its weapons.
